@node ClassAct

     ClassAct is a layout system designed to be simple, small, yet powerful.
CamWatch's configuration window requires ClassAct.  You can get it off the web
from http://classact.warped.com/

@endnode

@node Revision

CamWatch 1.1 -- Release 14-Oct-97
---------------------------------
Sheesh.  24 hours after release and I'm already getting reports from people.
Bug fix round 2:
- Fixed CamWatch not liking the NCSA web server, and probably others
- Cleaned up the prefs page
- Added a needed "Save", "Use", "Cancel" button to the configuration window
- Save/Load default config now assumes the .cfg you give on the command line
  (if you give one) is the default config file.
- Fixed MAJOR bug with CamWatch not liking non-graphics-card systems

CamWatch 1.0.1 -- Released 14-Oct-97
------------------------------------
- Fixed configuration window, enabled the file selector gadget and uses page
  tabs now.
- Fixed some weird combinations of file save options and other options causing
  problems with CamWatch NEVER deleting files.

CamWatch 1.0 -- Released 13-Oct-97
----------------------------------
- Initial release

@endnode
